Mozilla/5.0 (X11; Linux i686; rv:7.0a2) Gecko/20110706 Firefox/7.0a2

Firefox exists unexpectedly when accessing 
http://tvonline.isfree.org/eurosport-live/

with the following error message in the terminal:

./firefox/firefox: symbol lookup error: /usr/lib/mozilla/plugins/libvlcplugin.so: undefined symbol: NPP_Initialize


This is not a crash considering that there are no entries in about:crashes.
